title: Leaves from the journal of our life in the Highlands, from 1848 to 1861 :
author: Victoria
snippet: Then we passed the point of Logierait,where there are the remains of an ancient castle, —the old Regality Court of the Dukes of Athole.

title: The Edinburgh gazetteer, or geographical dictionary ...
snippet: Logierait, a parish of Scotland, inPerthshire, in the form of an irregulartriangle, about 7 miles on each side.
